	<h1 class="title">Storefront Help</h1>

	<p style="padding: 0 15px; font-size: 0.8em;">Congratulations on your new Storefront! We have set up this page to provide you with some helpful 
		information to get your Storefront set up and ready for use. Your Storefront provides an excellent means for you to highlight 
		your active listings and draw more customer attention. Your basic Storefront features and capabilities include:</p>
