			<li>Upload your Logo</li>
			<li>Select a Pre-Made Theme to match your Logo</li>
			<li>Create your own Storefront Categories</li>
			<li>Create your own "Additional Pages" to use for About Us, Contact Us, etc.</li>
			<li>Send a Newsletter to subscribers of your StoreFront</li>
